    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'it''s freezing out here

    but so calm

    the forest is closing behind
    us

    I can hear the river

    that once swallowed you


    now it''s asking

    "touch
    me with your hand"


    reminding me

    about the rose

    that was raised
    from stone

    cut off by words

    buried in water

    and turned into prose

    by
    my desire'
